Body:
Our 15th Cosy Club, now part of the collection opened to the public on 22nd August 2016, a Cosy little outdoor terrace area welcomes you along. Just inside, a glass staircase takes you to the top where you'll be greeted by our wonderful hosts. Disabled access and for those with buggies, can be gained through entering the shopping centre to the side and using the lift , we have just as glorious of an entrance from inside the centre too.
Our glorious dark wooden bar is almost the length of the restaurant complimented by golden rails where you can lean and watch over our team whip you up the perfect drink. Just behind this glorious scene lays our restaurant, tucked away and overlooked by our hand carved wooden wall, originally made of stone and recreated for your viewing pleasure.
Did we mention the presence of our illuminating chandeliers? You'll be sure to find something delightful to look at on every wall. Look out for a rather dashing looking chap in a suit, with a long face&hellip;
